    dc:creator "Barboza, Gloria E.", "Knapp, Sandra", "Saerkinen, Tiina" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "A revision of the South American species of the Morelloid clade (Solanum L., Solanaceae)" ;
    bibo:endPage "342" ;
    bibo:journal "PhytoKeys" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2023-08-29" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "231" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure12>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure13>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure14>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure2> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Solanum aloysiifolium A flowering and fruiting branch B flower C calyx D dissected flower E stamen, dorsal view F stamen, ventral view G gynoecium H fruit I seed (A-I Barboza et al. 1072). Illustration by L. Ribulgo." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897473" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Solanum aloysiifolium A habit B inflorescence in bud C flowers at full anthesis D fully mature fruits (A Barboza et al. 3506 B Barboza et al. 3566 C Barboza et al. 3565 D Barboza et al. 3532). Photos by S. Knapp." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897474" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure14>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Distribution map of Solanum aloysiifolium." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897475" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.231.100894.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Representative habits and leaves of South American morelloids A prostrate annual herbs (S. weddellii) B large lax shrubs (S. aloysiifolium) C roots forming along a creeping stem (S. juninense) D spinose processes on stems of many species (S. huayavillense) E glandular trichomes found in some members of the clade (S. glandulosipilosum) F dendritic / branched trichomes found in S. pallidum G regularly 3 - lobed leaves in S. palitans H highly variable leaves along a single stem in S. salicifolium (A Saerkinen et al. 4038 B Barboza et al. 3505 C Saerkinen et al. 4754 D Barboza et al. 3536 E Barboza et al. 3520 F Saerkinen et al. 4010 G Atchison & Gagnon 25 H Barboza et al. 3473). Photos by S. Knapp, G. Atchison, and T. Saerkinen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/897463" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

